19
00:00:17,647 --> 00:00:19,482
<i>Darkness on Dagobah!</i>

20
00:00:19,733 --> 00:00:22,027
<i>All attention is focused on Yoda,</i>

21
00:00:22,110 --> 00:00:25,197
<i>who claims
to hear the voice of a long-dead Jedi.</i>

22
00:00:25,947 --> 00:00:28,283
<i>Convinced that he is guided
by Qui-Gon Jinn,</i>

23
00:00:28,992 --> 00:00:30,911
<i>he finds five priestesses</i>

24
00:00:30,994 --> 00:00:35,040
<i>who will teach him how
to manifest consciousness after death.</i>

25
00:00:35,874 --> 00:00:39,294
<i>After many trials,
Yoda travels to Moraband,</i>

26
00:00:39,419 --> 00:00:42,214
<i>ancient home planet of the Sith.</i>

27
00:00:42,297 --> 00:00:46,301
<i>For now he must face the true evil
that may be his undoing</i>

28
00:00:46,801 --> 00:00:49,971
<i>and one that seeks
to control the galaxy.</i>

29
00:00:55,185 --> 00:00:56,770
Careful, we must be.

30
00:00:56,853 --> 00:01:01,399
Deserted, this planet was,
long ago, after many wars.

31
00:01:41,022 --> 00:01:43,441
Again, leave you, I must, my friend.

32
00:01:43,692 --> 00:01:45,485
Guard the ship, you will.

33
00:01:46,152 --> 00:01:50,782
If return, I do not, by three night falls,
take the ship to Coruscant, you shall.

34
00:01:51,032 --> 00:01:53,201
Tell them of where I went.

35
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:07,609
We are the Sith.

36
00:03:08,151 --> 00:03:10,445
Afraid of you, I am not.

37
00:03:10,779 --> 00:03:12,697
We shall see.

38
00:03:38,139 --> 00:03:41,601
There is no life after death.

39
00:03:42,227 --> 00:03:44,771
Only nothingness awaits you, Jedi.

40
00:03:46,272 --> 00:03:49,651
Your fear feeds our hunger for power.

41
00:03:51,236 --> 00:03:54,906
They will know you are here,
we will tell them.

42
00:03:56,282 --> 00:03:59,702
You will die and be nothing.

43
00:04:09,170 --> 00:04:13,133
Sir, you have been ordered
to go to Coruscant immediately.

44
00:04:13,508 --> 00:04:16,636
Tell Lord Sidious I am on my way.

45
00:05:23,411 --> 00:05:28,082
Why do you come to my tomb, Jedi?

46
00:05:28,791 --> 00:05:30,084
To learn.

47
00:05:30,168 --> 00:05:33,254
Do you know who I am?

48
00:05:34,297 --> 00:05:35,298
Yes.

49
00:05:35,423 --> 00:05:38,968
Darth Bane,
the ancient Sith Lord, you are.

50
00:05:39,677 --> 00:05:43,223
And know why I am not forgotten?

51
00:05:43,765 --> 00:05:46,351
Created the Rule of Two, you did.

52
00:05:47,435 --> 00:05:50,313
The Sith killed each other.

53
00:05:50,396 --> 00:05:53,566
Victims of their own greed.

54
00:05:53,733 --> 00:05:58,988
But from the ashes of destruction,
I was the last survivor.

55
00:05:59,447 --> 00:06:03,201
I chose to pass my knowledge
on to only one.

56
00:06:03,576 --> 00:06:10,124
I created a legacy so resilient
that now you come before me.

57
00:06:12,293 --> 00:06:14,921
Have you come to be my apprentice?

58
00:06:15,505 --> 00:06:19,342
You must kill me to gain my place.

59
00:06:20,635 --> 00:06:22,887
Dead, you are, already.

60
00:06:25,682 --> 00:06:28,685
Then what stands before you?

61
00:06:28,977 --> 00:06:30,395
An illusion.

62
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:32,772
Real, you are not.

63
00:06:33,815 --> 00:06:37,277
-You do not fear me?
-No.

64
00:06:37,443 --> 00:06:39,195
Exist, you do not, anymore.

65
00:06:49,163 --> 00:06:50,582
<i>Yoda.</i>

66
00:06:52,667 --> 00:06:54,502
<i>Yoda.</i>

67
00:07:20,778 --> 00:07:24,115
I sense we have a great opportunity

68
00:07:24,198 --> 00:07:28,244
to strike a deadly blow
to the Jedi Order.

69
00:07:28,828 --> 00:07:31,831
But we must act swiftly.

70
00:08:09,827 --> 00:08:12,163
A warning, I must give you.

71
00:08:12,497 --> 00:08:13,498
Yes.

72
00:08:13,581 --> 00:08:17,418
All your trials you have faced
have been our doing.

73
00:08:18,127 --> 00:08:20,588
And you have passed them well.

74
00:08:21,214 --> 00:08:25,009
But inside, there is a place
where we have no control.

75
00:08:25,510 --> 00:08:30,640
For it is a place of absolute darkness.

76
00:08:31,099 --> 00:08:32,809
What happened here?

77
00:08:33,267 --> 00:08:37,188
It is the chamber
where the Sith would sacrifice Jedi.

78
00:08:37,271 --> 00:08:40,692
The Sith of your time will find you there.

79
00:08:41,567 --> 00:08:43,611
And you will find them.

80
00:08:44,529 --> 00:08:49,117
Be careful, for what they may offer
will certainly feel like an answer.

81
00:09:08,302 --> 00:09:12,140
Only the presence of someone
significant to you

82
00:09:12,265 --> 00:09:17,812
would allow you to sense this
ripple through time and space.

83
00:09:18,855 --> 00:09:22,150
My old master, Yoda!

84
00:09:22,817 --> 00:09:24,527
Yes,

85
00:09:24,610 --> 00:09:28,406
Master Yoda has come to Moraband,

86
00:09:28,489 --> 00:09:31,743
although why, I do not know.

87
00:09:32,243 --> 00:09:35,246
We shall, however, use the strong bond

88
00:09:35,329 --> 00:09:38,875
that once existed
between you and your master

89
00:09:38,958 --> 00:09:44,046
to allow us to see things
that we otherwise could not.

90
00:09:44,672 --> 00:09:46,758
How can this be done, Master?

91
00:09:47,175 --> 00:09:51,262
It is an old art of the dark side.

92
00:09:51,721 --> 00:09:55,600
Now, hold out your hand, Apprentice.

93
00:09:59,771 --> 00:10:04,317
I need but a drop for the ritual to begin.

94
00:10:30,718 --> 00:10:33,971
Now, concentrate on Master Yoda,

95
00:10:34,055 --> 00:10:38,226
bring all your focus to him.

96
00:10:38,726 --> 00:10:41,395
But will he not sense our presence?

97
00:10:45,316 --> 00:10:48,736
We shall come to him
with a familiar face,

98
00:10:49,153 --> 00:10:51,447
a long-lost face.

99
00:10:52,114 --> 00:10:55,284
One he would be eager to see again,

100
00:10:55,868 --> 00:11:00,081
one whom he would ask
and want answered

101
00:11:00,456 --> 00:11:04,710
all the questions he seeks.

102
00:11:14,095 --> 00:11:15,888
Help me.

103
00:11:18,182 --> 00:11:21,602
Please, please free me.

104
00:11:22,270 --> 00:11:25,731
Sifo-Dyas? Alive, you are!

105
00:11:26,607 --> 00:11:29,735
Help me please, Yoda.

106
00:11:30,820 --> 00:11:34,323
I have been imprisoned for so long.

107
00:11:35,825 --> 00:11:37,618
Know who did this to you?

108
00:11:40,454 --> 00:11:44,834
What if I could tell you
who the Sith Lord is?

109
00:11:45,626 --> 00:11:48,754
Free me and I will reveal it.

110
00:11:48,838 --> 00:11:49,922
No!

111
00:11:51,299 --> 00:11:55,636
He knows how to achieve
what you seek.

112
00:11:55,970 --> 00:11:58,723
Captivated by the physical realm,
the Sith are.

113
00:11:58,806 --> 00:12:00,474
What else is there?

114
00:12:01,225 --> 00:12:07,148
Free me and together
we can know who the Sith Lord is.

115
00:12:07,899 --> 00:12:10,818
Gain the power you deserve,

116
00:12:11,652 --> 00:12:13,613
and save the future.

117
00:12:14,030 --> 00:12:17,366
-No.
-You must free me!

118
00:12:17,742 --> 00:12:20,119
Nothing to show me, the Sith have.

119
00:12:20,703 --> 00:12:23,331
We shall see.

120
00:12:30,838 --> 00:12:31,964
Sidious!

121
00:12:41,557 --> 00:12:44,685
There is no question,
the ship was carrying Count Dooku.

122
00:12:45,144 --> 00:12:46,145
We've scanned the area

123
00:12:46,228 --> 00:12:48,773
and he is meeting with someone
inside the building.

124
00:12:48,856 --> 00:12:50,107
Thanks, Rex.

125
00:12:50,191 --> 00:12:53,778
-Master Yoda, what are your orders?
-Orders?

126
00:12:53,861 --> 00:12:55,988
Are you all right, Master?

127
00:12:56,072 --> 00:12:58,658
-Where am I?
-I don't understand.

128
00:12:58,741 --> 00:13:00,326
Tell me, you must!

129
00:13:00,409 --> 00:13:02,662
The industrial sector on Coruscant.

130
00:13:02,870 --> 00:13:04,330
What is happening here?

131
00:13:04,413 --> 00:13:06,624
A rogue shuttle
slipped through the security grid.

132
00:13:06,707 --> 00:13:09,377
-We suspect Dooku was on board.
-And?

133
00:13:09,502 --> 00:13:13,881
Master, this is your mission.
Are you sure you're all right?

134
00:13:13,965 --> 00:13:16,384
Clouded, the dark side has made me.

135
00:13:16,717 --> 00:13:18,844
Tell me, who is inside?

136
00:13:19,095 --> 00:13:21,973
We intercepted a transmission
calling Dooku to Coruscant.

137
00:13:22,056 --> 00:13:25,643
We believe he is meeting with
his master, the Sith Lord.

138
00:13:26,060 --> 00:13:29,397
Feel it, I do. Feel their power.

139
00:13:30,189 --> 00:13:31,983
Your orders, Master?

140
00:13:32,066 --> 00:13:33,693
Capture them, we will.

141
00:13:33,776 --> 00:13:37,238
The time has come to discover
the identity of this Sith Master.

142
00:13:37,571 --> 00:13:40,616
-And if they escape?
-Escape, not.

143
00:13:40,700 --> 00:13:44,620
If it comes to it, execute them, we must.

144
00:13:44,996 --> 00:13:47,331
End it now, we will.

145
00:14:04,765 --> 00:14:06,100
Move in.

146
00:14:11,647 --> 00:14:13,357
I've got two confirmed targets.

147
00:14:13,774 --> 00:14:15,985
Be ready for additional unfriendlies.

148
00:14:26,746 --> 00:14:30,249
It appears we have company.

149
00:14:33,419 --> 00:14:34,795
Take them!

150
00:14:51,562 --> 00:14:54,982
We meet at last, Darth Sidious.

151
00:14:55,274 --> 00:14:59,570
You cannot stop what is to come.

152
00:15:10,372 --> 00:15:12,249
Skywalker, no!

153
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:09,223
No!

154
00:16:54,810 --> 00:16:59,607
Save him, Jedi? Can you save him?

155
00:17:13,204 --> 00:17:15,331
Why not let him go?

156
00:17:15,581 --> 00:17:20,628
Let him die
and you can stop all that I will do.

157
00:17:24,924 --> 00:17:25,966
No!

158
00:17:26,300 --> 00:17:28,302
The future is not yours yet.

159
00:17:30,137 --> 00:17:32,181
Tempted, I will not be.

160
00:17:32,264 --> 00:17:34,934
Sacrifice all, I am ready to do.

161
00:18:39,999 --> 00:18:43,711
We have failed to break Master Yoda.

162
00:18:44,211 --> 00:18:45,921
He is strong.

163
00:18:46,422 --> 00:18:52,177
We will need more time
if we are to defeat him and the Jedi.

164
00:18:55,681 --> 00:18:57,099
Yoda.

165
00:18:59,184 --> 00:19:01,228
Come back to us, Yoda.

166
00:19:04,315 --> 00:19:05,357
Died, have I?

167
00:19:06,317 --> 00:19:07,651
In a way.

168
00:19:10,779 --> 00:19:12,948
Now does my training begin.

169
00:19:13,907 --> 00:19:16,452
The one you know as Qui-Gon Jinn

170
00:19:16,535 --> 00:19:19,455
will commune with you
and guide your training.

171
00:19:19,538 --> 00:19:24,001
Like us, you shall learn to maintain
your consciousness after death.

172
00:19:24,293 --> 00:19:26,170
Enlightenment.

173
00:19:26,962 --> 00:19:28,172
Spirit.

174
00:19:29,214 --> 00:19:30,341
Balance.

175
00:19:30,883 --> 00:19:34,178
There is another Skywalker.

176
00:19:34,261 --> 00:19:38,474
There is another Skywalker?

177
00:19:50,444 --> 00:19:54,156
Yes, time to go home, it is.

178
00:20:26,063 --> 00:20:30,818
The Council has assembled,
they are eager to hear your report.

179
00:20:31,318 --> 00:20:34,363
Afraid not much there is
to say of my journey.

180
00:20:37,741 --> 00:20:40,369
So, nothing significant
happened to you out there?

181
00:20:40,494 --> 00:20:42,329
Yes and no.

182
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:45,207
To the end, we are coming now.

183
00:20:45,666 --> 00:20:49,503
Did your journey give you insight
on how to win the war?

184
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:54,174
No longer certain
that one ever does win a war, I am.

185
00:20:55,050 --> 00:20:57,803
For in fighting the battles,
the bloodshed,

186
00:20:58,637 --> 00:21:00,431
already lost, we have.

187
00:21:01,098 --> 00:21:03,517
Yet, open to us, a path remains,

188
00:21:04,768 --> 00:21:06,854
that, unknown to the Sith, is.

189
00:21:07,604 --> 00:21:10,566
Through this path,
victory we may yet find.

190
00:21:11,608 --> 00:21:13,861
Not victory in the Clone Wars,

191
00:21:14,236 --> 00:21:17,531
but victory for all time.

192
00:21:17,555 --> 00:21:19,555
http://hiqve.com/

